name: Lilly the raccoon rattle
description:
A raccoon's skull painted a deep purple with yellow and green accents. To celebrate the coming of spring and color, she will sing for you if you help her dance. 

With a jewel adorning her forehead, she will be noticed long before she even makes a sound.

name: Jaiden the adorned bobcat
description:
Adorned with precious gems, Jaiden is a royal, yet classy addition to the plethora of skulls on display. His teeth are perfect and shine silver, where his bones are painted a contrasting black, setting apart the shining jewels on his forehead. 

He will be a wonderful, regal addition to your display or cabinet.

name: Julian the bobcat
description:
A striking, vivid piece. Julian is a complete bobcat skull adorned with gold leaf and a pair of rubies. 

With two holes in her head, she was fitted with these gems to complete her. Decorated around them are the colors of fire and serenity. 

Open or closed, she will be a stunning piece in anyone's display.

name: Dominique the coyote
description:
A coyote skull decorated lovingly with paints and gold leaf. 

Reminiscent of Pacific Islander sculptures, it will be sure to help you when you need a guardian guide.

name: Deer Jaw Assembly
description:
A deer jaw decorated with hand-painted flowers and hung with ribbons, twines, and trinkets. The entire piece is balanced by a pair of large turkey feathers. 

US only.

name: Stories from the Grapevine
description:
A cow jaw carved with the image of a howling wolf and flowing grapevines. 

Meticulously carved and stained, this piece is durable and will last for years. 

Before the written word, stories were passed on through speech. As generations went on, children would hear the stories over and over through their parents, friends, and relatives. I wanted to run along the theme of the grapevine and communication.

name: Stone and glass memory wire bracelets
description:
A variety of stones and beads are available for your choosing. 

These are memory wire bracelets that are stackable and fit most people. They're shiny and easy to put on! 

Opalite, blue goldstone, goldstone, mixed colors, feel free to message me and I can show you what colors I have :)

name: Atlas
description: A tiny skunk atlas bone painted black and silver and hung on a silver chain.

name: Leather Pouch
description:
A callback to that started me here, this medicine pouch is made of very soft glove grade buckskin leather. 

Not only does it hold things in the pouch, itself, but it also has a small charm that opens and an hold tiny, tiny objects. 

Treat yourself to this durable, functional piece that will last for years to come. 

Pouch measures about 3 inches tall, fringe is another inch or so.

name: Little Axis
description:
A striped skunk axis bone with vibrant Opalite and a blue glass bead that dangles from the bottom. 

A classy, subtle accent piece about an inch tall. Comes with an 18 inch chain.

name: Maxillary Charm
description:
A silver raccoon maxilla and zygomatic arch adorned with a dangling glass charm. 

comes with an 18 inch chain.

name: Quartz and Bone Necklace
description: A red fox vertebra accented with a quartz point and a blue goldstone bead. Comes with a silver chain.

name: Fox Axis
description: A painted and sealed Red Fox axis on a siver chain. Accented by Opalite and Blue Goldstone, this is definitely a piece that will bring you subtle attention.

name: Swimming in Pink
description:
This chain necklace features a wire-wrapped qurtz piece dangling below two spheres of rose quarts and a fish bone. 

Classy and simple, this necklace will definitely add a subtle flair to your outfit.

name: Leather and bone choker
description: Made with very soft buckskin lace and bone beads, this necklace will accent your outfit and give you a natural, of-the-earth vibe.

name: Purple glass rosary with wire pieces and laboradorite
description: Made with tough hemp cord, purple glass beads, laboradorite beads, and wire middle and end pieces, this handcrafted piece is meant to be a great carrying piece. Flexible, durable, and light.

name: Wolf Moon Dangle Earrings
description:
These sterling silver wolves will deck out your face as they howl to the moons that you can adjust! 

Whether it's new moon, full moon, or anything in between, you can rotate the crackled glass beads to your heart's content. 

Wolves are detailed on both sides.

name: Lotus painted bobcat skull
description:
Lovingly stippled with acrylic paint and dyed in lavender tea, this bobcat skull will fit right in with a collection. It has all its teeth, and is entirely intact. 

Due to customs I can only ship within the US. Please make sure that bobcat parts are legal in your state.

name: Bone bead chain rosary with laboradorite
description:
A rosary made of polished bone beads with laboradorite beads between each decade. The laboradorite beads shine in the light as you turn them. 

Half of the proceeds go toward supplying additional rosary materials for the priest who taught me to make them.

name: Small elk hide clutch
description:
11x16.5 cm. 

This elk skin clutch is a durable choice for all your little everyday carry items. Cut and bound with elk hide and accented with glass crow beads. Closed with a gear button. 

Durable, stretchable, and small enough to carry around. Built with a braided leather loop for ease of carrying.

name: Soft buckskin stone pouch with black wolf fur
Anatomical head - Bobcat
description:
An anatomical model of bobcat facial musculature. 

Hand sculpted and hand painted on a genuine bobcat skull.

name: American Savannah
description:
Zebra-print cowhide embellished with coyote bones. This backpack is built to withstand time and abuse as all leather can. 

Backpack can hold a standard textbook, tablet, and medium laptops.

name: Blue Goldstone Claw Necklace
description:
Chain necklace with a blue goldstone pendant and a genuine claw. 

Will stand up to everyday use, the pendant is entirely reversible.

Options include Porcupine or Coyote claws. The porcupine claw is the longer of the two.

name: Ancient Royalty
description:
A genuine Grey Fox skull hand-carved in relief. A blue opal piece adorns its forehead, bringing focus to its center. Stained with teas and spices. 

This skull was missing a few teeth when I bought it, but most of its teeth are still intact. Please feel free to message me with any questions! :)

name: Giraffe Kitchen towel
description:
flour sack Kitchen Towels 4pk. 30”x30” 
100% cotton
machine wash warm
tumble dry low

name: Genesis Carved Skull
description:
A hand-carved skull decorated with concentric circles, carved ribbons, pomegranates, and a tree with a snake wound around it. 

Intended for use with a light through the back to show all details.

name: Coyote tooth braided necklace with glass crow beads
description:
A simple necklace made of braided waxed chord, adjustable to any size. The pendant is a coyote canine tooth braided in with the necklace and surrounded by four glass beads, two on each side. 

Tooth has a slight crack in it, though it adds to the character and does not affect its durability.

name: Yellow Agate Wire Wrapped Pendant
description:
A small piece of yellow agate wrapped in bronze wire. 

Chain not included. Perfect for a subtle accessory.

name: Green Agate Wire Wrapped Pendant
description:
A piece of wire-wrapped green agate. Chain is not included. 

Perfect for a natural accept to your outfit!

name: Red Turquoise wire wrapped pendant
description:
Pendant only, chain not included. 

Two pieces of red turquoise perfect for a natural accent to your outfit. 

Available in bronze and silver wire.

name: Moonstone Chip Bracelet
description:
A moonstone chip bracelet made to fit small to medium wrists 

Links can be added or removed free of charge.

name: Coyote Fur Shoulder Messenger Bag
description:
A medium sized shoulder bag made from recycled leather and a coyote pelt. Flap closure ensures that your belongings don't fall out. 

Can fit any item with regular iPad dimensions. 

Lined and durable, this piece is great for day to day use and will definitely be a head-turner!

name: Re-Flection: Coyote skull rattle
description:
A unique piece with personality. A coyote skull whose orbit was damaged, the hole has been filled with an iridescent glass bead and the reflection is depicted scattering across it's surface. 

A light rattle, perfect for quieter meditation or simply for lower-key noise making.

name: Fortune the bobcat
description:
Fortune will chase away the evil spirits that want to take your money away! Her lucky coin eye will draw in wealth, while her dreamcatcher eye traps the nightmares and ghosts that want to stop you. 

She is also fond of mice.

name: Porcupine claw, amethyst, leather tassel necklace
description:
Made with real copper-wire wrapped porcupine claw accompanied by a recovered leather tassel and an amethyst bead. 

Great for a more natural glam or a reminder of the wonderful digging powers of the porcupine.

name: Buffalo tooth hemp necklace with antique wood beads
description:
Antique buffalo teeth strung on three hemp chords with antique wooden beads. Knots on either side keep the pendants from sliding around. The ends of the cord have glass beads. 

The necklace can be tied around the neck to be a choker or a hanging necklace.

name: Black Jewel: Coyote Skull
description: A painted iridescent coyote skull. A unique addition to a curiosity shelf or any display.

name: Coyote tooth rosary
description:
Interspersed with a wide array of colors, this rosary is made with 53 coyote teeth following the rosary pattern of five decades, six spacers, and a set of three beads before the cross. 

Completely functional as a rosary for a wide variety of beliefs. Jump ring allows for easy removal of the cross for substitution of any other totem.

name: Coyote tooth necklace with glass beads
description:
A small coyote tooth with glass beads flanking it. 

Hemp cord is knotted at both ends to prevent slipping 

Adjustable to choker length or longer.

name: Fox Fur and Leather Purse
description:
This is a hand-sewn custom patterned purse made from a vintage white fox fur. The lining is faux leather, the leather is split vegetable-tanned leather. 

The strap is secured with rivets. The purse string is suede with a brass buckle and steel rivets. 

Tested and it's pretty sturdy. The purse itself is about eight inches wide and six and a half inches tall. 

Strap is slightly adjustable. Not long enough to be cross-body.

name: Cute Aquatic Themed Painted Skull
description: Bear skull painted in shades of blue to reflect an aquatic theme, or possibly even similar to the native tribes in the movie Avatar, which is where I drew my inspiration from.

name: Rhinestone buffalo teeth on braided cord
description:
Antiqued buffalo teeth threaded on braided hemp cord. Teeth are accented with clear rhinestones. 

Natural materials (except rhinestones), general neutral color

name: Three-strand braided coyote tooth necklace
description: Braided hemp cord gives way to three beaded strands of different length gracing your neck comfortably. Natural materials, mild colors.

name: Small Painted Coyote Skull Rattle Blue White
description:
A hand-painted rattle made of a coyote skull top and beads. Holes leading to the cranium have been sealed to prevent the Beads from spilling out.

Use these for ceremonies, drum circles, collections, or hang it on your wall. 

Piece is about 7" long and has coyote teeth tassels tied with hemp rope and leather.

name: Painted Gray Fox Skull Diamond pattern chic
description:
A small Gray Fox skull painted with browns and purples in a chic diamond pattern. It's a subtle way of having a unique piece in your collection without attracting too much attention among your other objects. 

Skull has been sealed with a fixative. Hand-painted.

name: Beaded hemp choker
description: A braided multicolor hemp choker. Tie it to loop it around your neck or wrap it a few times to make a bracelet.

name: Buffalo tooth necklace and bracelet set with wooden beads
description:
The necklace has an antiqued buffalo tooth hanging between two antique wooden beads. The necklace can be tied at any length. 

The bracelet has an antique wooden bead and is braided on matching hemp cord. The bracelet is adjustable. 

These are sold as a set.

name: Rose Painted Nutria Skull
description:
I'm not actually sure what it is. It's not beaver. 

Anyway. A skull painted green with rose patterns on it. Hand-painted in acrylics and sprayed with fixative. 

Skull has no incisors, but has it's full set of molars. No lower jaw.

name: Jester Painted Coyote Skull
description:
A unique sort of painted skull. Jester is a bright piece with his own definite personality. 

Genuine, nearly perfect coyote skull. He will make a great addition to any curio collection!

name: Amethyst Cone Shell Charm Necklace
description:
Carry a piece of the sea with you with a purple cone shell necklace on an amethyst cord. 

Wire-wrapped and tested durable, the shell won't fall off.

Created by Hiseas Jewelry.

name: Pair of wire-wrapped porcupine claws
description:
This is a paired set of claws wrapped in copper wire. Carefully wound and mirrored, this is perfect for you and your nature-loving friends or a pair who wants something a little different. 

Genuine porcupine claws wrapped in copper wire.

name: Leather medicine pouch with fox/wolf charm
description:
This little pouch is designed to hold any little trinket(s) you feel you need close to you. The pouch is 2 inches tall with about 1.75 inches of holding space. 

The charm is sterling silver. 

Pouch and fringes are dyed lambskin, pouch is a drawstring and can be held closed with a bead on the necklace itself. 

Beads are glass crow beads. 

Can be used for carrying stones, coins, fetishes, prayers, anything you like.

name: Small Steam Coyote Pouch
description:
A tiny pouch for your small items. Keep a ring or a tiny memento inside! Hang it around your neck, tie it to your belt, or hang it from your pack. 

Gear is taken from a vintage clock, loop closure. 

Scrap upholstery leather, scrap coyote fur, suede cord. 

Cord is 63 cm in circumference

Pouch is 2 x 3 cm

name: Leather pouch with front pocket
description:
Cowhide leather bag measures 2.25" x 4". Has an outer pocket that can be used for quick access.

Recycled coyote fur trim on front.

Drawstring closure, can be held in place by bone bead. Closes from one side. 

Can be used as a medicine bag, fetish pouch, or for any small things you'd like to carry with you.

Cord has 16" circumference.

name: Porcupine claw pendant w/copper wire and glass beads
description:
This claw is more in sync with beaded regalia or the boho look. The claw can be flipped on either side; one side has the copper swirls and the other has an array of glass beads. 

Genuine porcupine claw wrapped in copper wire embellished with small glass beads.

name: Adjustable porcupine claw choker
description:
Seven nice, long porcupine claws strung on a hemp cord and separated by striped jasper beads. 

Perfect for pow-wows, casual style, and for anyone who wants a conversation piece around their neck.
